data.description: The craftmanship of this home will not disappoint. This one of a kind home is not only stunning but built and maintained to last. Sitting on over 5 acres, this 'castle like' build with the front turret gives this home an estate feel. Just minutes away from Erie for convenance yet offering the seclusion you want. It is complete with an automated, whole house generator. First floor Primary suit with a double door entry, large soaker tub, walk in closet, and sliders to the deck off the back of the home. Second floor has 3 bedrooms, 2 more full bathrooms and a sitting area off the balcony overlooking the large great room. Updated kitchen with two-sided fireplace. Current owner has made many updates in their ownership. A list has been provided with the Disclosures. Truly a must see!
